NAME

DateTime::Locale::wae_CH - Locale data examples for the Walser Switzerland (wae-CH) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Walser Switzerland locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Zištag, 5. Hornig 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Fritag, 22. Chrištmánet 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Samštag, 15. Herbštmánet -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. Hornig 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. Chrištmánet 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. Herbštmánet -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. Hor 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. Chr 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. Her -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008-02-05
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12-22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09-15
